SUPPORT

There are two options available for support for the Amberdms Billing System:

1. Commercial Support from Amberdms Ltd
	
   Amberdms provide a range of support offerings, for details please
   visit www.amberdms.com/billing


2. Support from the open source community

   You may be able to get assistance from other users and members of the
   open source community via the product mailing list, available at:

   http://lists.amberdms.com/mailman/listinfo/amberdms-bs


